The paper discusses environment perception in robotic and automotive applications, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also deals with sensor fusion and real-time implementation, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of Bayesian filters and stochastic models suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
